    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing almost as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with no chips or scratches, and the interior is pristine, featuring leather that looks and smells brand new. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a comprehensive service history and no issues whatsoever. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously maintained example in showroom state.",
